*** Only displaying a Col when the screen is medium or larger ex: (order of d-* matters)
<Row>
   <Col className='d-md-block d-sm-none'>
      ...
   </Col
   ...
</Row>

*** Hide a Col on small screen size but want to show on large screen:
 <Col sm={12} lg={4} className="d-none d-lg-block">
      {/* your content */}
 </Col>

